                ]
              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "伟大者帕西法尔",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>重击造成的伤害提升<span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">16/20/24/28/32%</span>；队伍中每存在一位与装备者元素类型相同的角色（包括装备者自身），将获得1层「手法」效果；每存在一位元素类型不同的角色，将获得1层「演技」效果。处于1/2/3层及以上「手法」效果下时，攻击力提升 <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">16%/32%/48%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">20%/40%/60% </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">24%/48%/72%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">28%/56%/84%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">32%/64%/96%</span>；处于1/2/3层及以上「演技」效果下时，移动速度提升<span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">4%/7%/10%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">6%/9%/12%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">8%/11%/14%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">10%/13%/16%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">12%/15%/18%</span>。</p>"
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
